OL,3,CMajority of victims don't believe
OL,4,Creporting crimes leads to justice
OL,6,FBut a new landmark survey by the
OL,7,FVictims' Commissioner shared
OL,8,Fexclusively with ITV News, reveals a
OL,9,Fpicture where victims are giving up on
OL,10,Fpolice, crimes are going unreported
OL,11,Fand there is a devastating lack of
OL,12,Fconfidence in the criminal justice
OL,13,Fsystem.
OL,15,FTake Ben Selvaratnam, a shop owner
OL,16,Fwhose convenience store is one of
OL,17,Fthose on the frontline of the
OL,18,Fshoplifting epidemic.
OL,20,FHe is fighting a losing battle against
OL,21,Fan ever more brazen band of thieves.
