OL,6,FIt's not only costing him hundreds of
OL,7,Fpounds a week but he is losing faith
OL,8,Fin the police who he says do nothing.
OL,10,FHe's given up and now doesn't even
OL,11,Fbother calling 999.
OL,13,F"We've been attacked. We've been
OL,14,Fassaulted verbally and physically. I
OL,15,Fmyself was bottled when I tried to
OL,16,Fconfront them and they used the
OL,17,Fbottles to smash us," he said.
