OL,6,F"We have to fend for ourselves," he
OL,7,Fcontinues. "We had an incident where
OL,8,F#50 of goods were stolen. The
OL,9,Fperpetrators, one of them was caught
OL,10,Foutside. We had CCTV, but the police
OL,11,Fdecided not to take anything further
OL,12,Fbecause, in their words, it was not in
OL,13,Fthe public interest. So more often
OL,14,Fthan not, we don't actually bother to
OL,15,Freport these incidents now."
OL,17,FAnd he is far from alone.
