OL,6,FBaroness Newlove became a campaigner
OL,7,Ffor victims after her husband, Garry,
OL,8,Fwas beaten to death outside their home
OL,9,Fin Warrington by youths vandalising
OL,10,Fher car.
OL,12,F"Are police failing victims?" I asked
OL,13,Fher.
OL,15,F"Yes," she said. "I think the time has
OL,16,Fcome, to actually look at the culture
OL,17,Falongside the policies... treat them
OL,18,Fvictims with respect and give their
OL,19,Fvoice some gravity and listen to what
OL,20,Fthey're saying."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
