OL,6,FFor years, Amy (not her real name) has
OL,7,Fbeen abused, harassed and intimidated
OL,8,Fby her neighbour.
OL,10,F"We had nails in our (car) tyre, we
OL,11,Fwere followed down the street at
OL,12,Fnight, he tried to grab us over the
OL,13,Ffence and tried to be inappropriate,"
OL,14,Fshe said. "He was trying to kill us,
OL,15,Femotionally... to crush us in every
OL,16,Fsense because we had dared to say no."
OL,18,FShe was targeted for being disabled
OL,19,Fand being part of the LGBTQ+ community.
