OL,6,FDespite numerous complaints to the
OL,7,Fpolice, she told ITV News that
OL,8,Finvestigations have gone nowhere.
OL,10,F"How would you sum up the police
OL,11,Fresponse?" I asked her.
OL,13,F"Inadequate, incompetent and
OL,14,Fdefensive," she replied. "It felt...
OL,15,Fif I'd called 999, no one would've
OL,16,Fcome. I could have had a major wound
OL,17,Fand no one would've showed. That's how
OL,18,Fit felt. It felt like they just did
OL,19,Fnot care about my life."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
