OL,6,FAnd would she feel comfortable phoning
OL,7,F999 and reporting a crime today, I put
OL,8,Fto her.
OL,10,F"No," she replied. "And I probably
OL,11,Fwouldn't. It's not worth it. They
OL,12,Fdon't listen."
OL,14,FBaroness Newlove said she isn't
OL,15,Fdepressed by the findings but
OL,16,Fdisappointed and angry, and desperate
OL,17,Fto change people's experiences.
OL,19,FShe said: "It's clear from the report
OL,20,Fthat too many get left behind, often
OL,21,Ffeeling frustrated and alone."
